snippet.title: Construction Simulator 2015 - Trailer
snippet.description: Construction Simulator 2015 includes a vehicle fleet of 15 construction machines and vehicles painstakingly modelled to reflect their real life counterparts by internationally well-known manufacturers such as LIEBHERR, MAN and STILL, an almost endless variety of building tasks wait to be tackled in a large, freely accessible environment.
